high_descs: Turn around and head right so you're in front of the center part of the couch.
Pick up the remote.
Turn right and walk to the purple chair.
Put the remote on the ottoman on top of the red object.
Turn around and walk around the left side of the coffee table to the other short side.
Pick the remote up off of the coffee table.
Walk ahead to the ottoman.
Put the remote on the ottoman to the left of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on an ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the sofa with two computers on it.
Pick up the controller from the sofa.
Turn around and walk over to the bench in front of the chair.
Put the controller on the bench.
Turn around and walk over to the brown table with the vase.
Pick up the controller from the brown table.
Walk back over to the bench.
Put the controller on the bench next to the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place two controllers on the bench in front of the couch.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the couch and turn left at the coffee table to face the couch.
Pick up the remote control in between the two laptop computers.
Turn right, hang a right at the end of the couch, turn right at the wall and turn around to face the ottoman of the chair.
Place the remote at the right corner of the ottoman on top of the red credit card.
Turn around, hang a right at the fireplace and turn right to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote to the right of the white vase.
Turn right, hang a left at the wall and walk to the ottoman of the chair.
Place the remote to the left of the other remote on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Place two remote controls on an ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the couch to your right.
Pick up the remote on the couch.
Carrying the remote, walk to the sofa seat on your right.
Place the remote on the sofa seat.
Turn around and walk to the coffee table to your left.
Pick up the remote on the table.
Carrying the remote, walk to the sofa seat straight ahead.
Place the remote next to the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Place remote one and two on the sofa seat.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the sofa with two computers.
Pick up the remote on the sofa between the two computers.
Turn right head towards the end of the coffee table, hang left towards the sofa stool.
Place the remote on the sofa stool on the bottom right edge.
Turn around and walk towards the other end of the coffee table.
Pick up the tv remote from the table next to the vase.
Head towards the sofa stool.
Place the remote to the left of the other remote on the stool.
anns.task_desc: Gather the two tv remotes to the sofa stool.

high_descs: Turn right, move around the coffee table then turn left and face the center of the couch.
Pick up the remote control located between the two laptops from the couch.
Turn right, move around the coffee table then turn left and face the ottoman in front of the chair.
Place the remote control on top of the red credit card on the front right corner of the ottoman.
Turn right, move around the ottoman past the fireplace, then move to and face the end of the coffee table closest to the fireplace.
Pick up the remote control to the right of the vase from the coffee table.
Turn left, move around the coffee table past the laptop and face the ottoman in front of the chair.
Place the remote control on the front center of the ottoman to the left of the remote control already there.
anns.task_desc: Place two remote controls on the ottoman.
